race.comment: SPENCER FURY (4) struggled for best form latest, finishing 7th (17.97) in a Grade 5 at Richmond Straight. Has won here at this journey. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. GO FORWARD SKIP (3) was strongly fancied to break through last time and justified the confidence with a maiden win at Richmond Straight over 324m (18.33). Has placed one times at this trip. Bold showing expected again. SHADY COYOTE (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished second (18.55) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Has a win and five minor placings from six starts from this draw. Racing well and deserves a win. ANJO TOPAZ (2) will make her presence felt on the back of recent top-three finishes.
